 and impressive end-product: just upload 8 images of your face, Vana develo=
ps a generative art model for you, and voila: a few hours later, you have a=
 gallery of AI-generated portraits emailed to you. Here=E2=80=99s one of mi=
ne:
Give it a try and tweet your favorite result @notboringco. We=E2=80=99ll re=
tweet a few of our favorites and share some in next week=E2=80=99s Weekly D=
ose.
That=E2=80=99s all for this week. Next Friday will be our 20th straight Wee=
